48Gl 2:19 "For through the Law I died to the Law, that I might live to God.
48Gl 2:20 "I have been crucified with Christ; and it is no longer I who live, but Christ lives in me; and the [life] which I now live in the flesh I live by faith in the Son of God, who loved me, and delivered Himself up for me.
