51Col 2:3 in whom are hidden all the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.
51Col 2:4 I say this in order that no one may delude you with persuasive argument.
51Col 2:5 For even though I am absent in body, nevertheless I am with you in spirit, rejoicing to see your good discipline and the stability of your faith in Christ.
