51Col 2:9 For in Him all the fulness of Deity dwells in bodily form,
51Col 2:10 and in Him you have been made complete, and He is the head over all rule and authority;
51Col 2:11 and in Him you were also circumcised with a circumcision made without hands, in the removal of the body of the flesh by the circumcision of Christ;
