621Jn 2:29 If you know that He is righteous, you know that everyone also who practices righteousness is born of Him.
621Jn 3:1 See how great a love the Father has bestowed upon us, that we should be called children of God; and [such] we are. For this reason the world does not know us, because it did not know Him.
621Jn 3:2 Beloved, now we are children of God, and it has not appeared as yet what we shall be. We know that, when He appears, we shall be like Him, because we shall see Him just as He is.
